snippet.title: Mallory and the Marble Sanctum Trailer
snippet.description:
Mallory and the Marble Sanctum, a free pre-alpha demo for a new, Unreal Engine 4 powered restart on my Mallory concept, is available for download! Explore an endless labyrinth on the edge of nowhere and find out if you're really as alone in it as you appear to be.

Play now on itch.io: https://khorrorshow.itch.io/mallory-marble-sanctum
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/BshQCFFwBz
